  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/95c9d459e90ef905a6a87ad2a690b399.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=134 /></span><br>Spend your in-game time with your friends!<br>The game supports an online co-op mode (up to 5 players).<br>There is also a proximity voice chat.<br>Help each other, split into roles, brew potions together!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/04a70b2e9660e14935cf06e45bf45dfe.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=134 /></span><br>The main goal of the game is to <strong>brew potions</strong> for your guests. There are two ways to sell your potions: active and passive.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Active selling</strong> - open a shop for a constant flow of guests for a given time and brew ordered potions. The success rate of completed orders will matter.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/7b166954a4894bf4232e00ad3b9f574f.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/7b166954a4894bf4232e00ad3b9f574f.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/7b166954a4894bf4232e00ad3b9f574f.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Passive selling</strong> - no need to rush, brew any potions you want and put them on the sale shelf.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/4316823bea983b4f4dbdda059145f8d5.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/4316823bea983b4f4dbdda059145f8d5.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/4316823bea983b4f4dbdda059145f8d5.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose the one that you like the most.<br><br><strong>Rivals</strong> are waiting for you. They sell potions, just like you. Get ready to interfere with each other!<br><br>Wander through the magical forest and <strong>collect ingredients</strong>. Brew potions from them or sell them to a trader!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/5c5862747604a7b44f3f49ae0d703673.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/5c5862747604a7b44f3f49ae0d703673.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/5c5862747604a7b44f3f49ae0d703673.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Build Mode</strong> lets you arrange in your house everything the way you want!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/196e5550daf1dec89fb60a2a18cc8b1d.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/196e5550daf1dec89fb60a2a18cc8b1d.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/196e5550daf1dec89fb60a2a18cc8b1d.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get new <strong>hairstyles and clothes</strong> with the earned gold and experiment with outfits.<br><br><strong>Happy brewing!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/95c9d459e90ef905a6a87ad2a690b399.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=134 /></span><br>Spend your in-game time with your friends!<br>The game supports an online co-op mode (up to 5 players).<br>There is also a proximity voice chat.<br>Help each other, split into roles, brew potions together!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/04a70b2e9660e14935cf06e45bf45dfe.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=134 /></span><br>The main goal of the game is to <strong>brew potions</strong> for your guests. There are two ways to sell your potions: active and passive.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Active selling</strong> - open a shop for a constant flow of guests for a given time and brew ordered potions. The success rate of completed orders will matter.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/7b166954a4894bf4232e00ad3b9f574f.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/7b166954a4894bf4232e00ad3b9f574f.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/7b166954a4894bf4232e00ad3b9f574f.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Passive selling</strong> - no need to rush, brew any potions you want and put them on the sale shelf.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/4316823bea983b4f4dbdda059145f8d5.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/4316823bea983b4f4dbdda059145f8d5.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/4316823bea983b4f4dbdda059145f8d5.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose the one that you like the most.<br><br><strong>Rivals</strong> are waiting for you. They sell potions, just like you. Get ready to interfere with each other!<br><br>Wander through the magical forest and <strong>collect ingredients</strong>. Brew potions from them or sell them to a trader!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/5c5862747604a7b44f3f49ae0d703673.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/5c5862747604a7b44f3f49ae0d703673.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/5c5862747604a7b44f3f49ae0d703673.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Build Mode</strong> lets you arrange in your house everything the way you want!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/196e5550daf1dec89fb60a2a18cc8b1d.poster.avif?t=1701606424\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/196e5550daf1dec89fb60a2a18cc8b1d.webm?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/196e5550daf1dec89fb60a2a18cc8b1d.mp4?t=1701606424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get new <strong>hairstyles and clothes</strong> with the earned gold and experiment with outfits.<br><br><strong>Happy brewing!</strong>",
